core

Class XMLFieldEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.XMLFieldEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class XMLFieldEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents an entry loaded from component XML descriptor files. Each XMLFieldEntry contains a variable type, the variable value stored in String objects.

    If the type is an enumeration (Enum), a base enum class is also required.

    Author:
    Istvan Fehervari
